            <div class="subfield">
               <div>
                  <p class="label"><strong>$c - Terms of availability</strong> 
                  </p>
                  <div>
                     <p>Price or a brief statement of availability and any paranthetical qualifying
                        information <span class="changed">about availability</span>.
                     </p>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                     <p>If only price information is present, data relevant to a single item is given in
                        one subfield $c in one field 020 and data relevant to another item is given in
                        another subfield $c in a subsequent 020 field.
                     </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="example">
                     <table>
